textAfterTable: HOW DO I REGISTER? REGISTRATION IS A 2-STEP PROCESS: STEP 1:  Register Online STEP 2:  Registration Form Drop-Off STEP 1: REGISTER ONLINE Please register at home; print the Registration Confirmation page; bring your Registration Confirmation page with you to one of the Registration Form Drop-off Dates to pay and complete your registration. We will only have a few computers onsite, so we recommend that you register online at home.     STEP 2: REGISTRATION FORM DROP-OFF To finalize your registration you will need to stop by the Cooper City Optimist Clubhouse (10500 Stirling Road) on one of the following dates to drop off the required documents and your payment for the registration fee.      Saturday, August 1, 2015  10:00 AM - 2:00 PM  Wednesday, August 5, 2015  6:00 PM - 8:00 PM  Saturday, August 8, 2015  10:00 AM - 2:00
